title: New: Joy Orbison – Sicko Cell
body:
[**Joy Orbison’s**](http://www.facebook.com/pages/Joy-Orbison/192924608912?ref=ts) new single is a dirty little treat. It’s gradually blinding and imposing, while eventually dropping into a garage/dubstep jam that we all know and love.  Stream below.

The track is out on [Hotflush](http://www.hotflushrecordings.com/).
